today...kinda sucked...no one was like mean or anything...i was just all stressed out and stuff....

i got home from school and realized i couldnt taste anything! like not the orange juice or the hot pocket i ate and i still cant taste the cinnamon toast crunch im eating haha. Joe (homeschooler) said that can happen if ur anxious or something....im not anxious about monday...just stressed...more scared...wont be in school guys....i still gotta get up kinda early too...the things at 830 til like 1 oh fun....kill me now.

store connected to it...and well first i remember like i had a lemon and i was with cam. and like eating the lemon and these people dropped like this huge thing on someones head (it was like in the to go down the stairs and jordan told Mary and Monica to run the oppisite way of me with her and they did and left me by myself ... and i like hate being alone... then i like walked around looknig for them and ended up in the store part and i remember seeing chas over there with some boys. and well i say down and like it was in the dark party of the store that was shut down and i heard people behind me talking about a camera that u can drop in the snow and it still work if u get the film developed within an hour then i like started runnign trying to get out of the store and i was running up escalators and stuff btut couldnt find a way out for awhile and finally i did and the dance was still going so i went in a computer room and got on and then my sister came in and started to like yell at me (dont totally remember what she was yelling) so i got off the computer and started crying. well Jordan was my ride home and she was gonig over to cams house and she told cam not to invite me so he didnt. and everyon left the dance with out me and i was left sitting in the cold at like midnight...so i started to like walk home alone and i was walkign past liek these condos and they were called "the vacation close to home" and it was for liek parents and people who needed a vacation but couldnt like just leave. and i knew my dad was in there so i was like passing all these buildings and the people were all staring at me with this blank stare as they watched me walk past and it was liek someone was in every single window stareing at me...then i found my dads and rung the door bell and he came to the door and locked it. and jsut gave me the same blank stare and  i started getting really scared...so i was running home. and when ireached my house nobody was there. so i walked in expecting my dogs to bark but htere was nothing no sound no nothing. i hate being home alone so i was gonna turn on some lights and tvs to make it seem liek i wasnt and when i went to press the buttom my whole intire house and everything like broke into pieces and dissappeared and i remember just sitting down. and that was when i "thought i woke up" and when i "woke up" i called George and told him how i hated Jordan and stuff (i dont really remember what was said) then i remember he hung up on me and thats when i woke up. i woke up at like 1030. tis gonna be impossible for me to sleep now....im like  creeped out and i know My jordy would never be that mean to me!!!! anyone know what my dream might mean?

my mom called while i was sleeping and left a message saying "Hey Lynn (my mid name) um its mom and i was just wondering what u were doing and if u wanna come over. um ill talk to u later love u bye" WHAT THE FUCK MOM dont call me saying i love u bye even if u do mean it...ugh i hate her. sgjnsdjkabfasjkfbas

Moms  still crazy and shes just gonna get worse and my sister wont stop talking to me abouit school and her grades i wonder if she even knows im not listening. Well i dunno. Im still confused about...well everything...Specially Joe....i love that kid. he is awesome...seriously. Dont think i can talk to him without smileing once....hes just like that....can make u smile....lol i cant be sad he makes it to hard lol.

ah my sister is still talkigng about her gym class...wow....

later xoxoxo

I was dissapointed that i didnt get to hang out with my Lexi babycakes all break. But ill see her in school tomorrow...woohoo.

but durring these last couple of weeks or so....ive learned who i can and cannot trust anymore...

Like everyone.
Trust no one.
